data.description: Get this one before it is gone!!  Beautiful 1 1/2 story home located on a lovely quiet street so close to everything! Upon entry you will feel the warmth of this open floor plan from the beauitful luxury plank flooring to the soaring vaults. The living room has a surround system in the closet that stays along with the TV, speakers and cameras!!  The kitchen features ample cabinet space, stainless steel appliances and a nice breakfast bar overlooking the dining area.  Leading from the dining area thru the patio doors is a beautiful deck that overlooks this HUGE treed lot that is fenced and offers so much privacy and serenity.The master suite on the main floor has ample space and features a nice sized walk in closet, full bath with double vanity.  Leading up the beautiful staircase are 2 bedrooms upstairs that have brand new carpeting, new trim and a full bath.  Partially finished lower level that has a nice walk out patio door to the lower level patio. Newer roof, newer AC and systems.
